{"tid":1180704,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解八達通出咗咁多年啲人都只係當佢係一張交通卡","createTime":"2019-06-01T04:57:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T08:52:37.000Z","uid":227275,"like":24,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fb05058aa34a24092f3fc2dc4d91145157f76f3b","tid":1180704,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T04:57:09.000Z","msg":"去惠康百佳買嘢班師奶永遠都係用現金<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n阿婆阿伯更加唔洗講 只係識用嚟搭兩蚊車<br />\n明明8達通一嘟就可以畀到錢 班師奶就係都要慢慢咁搵散紙 散銀 曬撚曬大家啲時間<br />\n佢哋平時只會用張八達通黎坐車<br />\n亦都好明顯係香港社會進步唔到嘅原因之一<br />\n<br />\n仲有就係超級市場上面嗰啲自助付款機呢 <br />\n就永遠都唔見到有人用 <br />\n但係排隊用現金畀錢嘅就成堆人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過都好嘅 咁我就唔使排隊可以直接畀錢走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問過佢哋點解咁鍾意比現金 聽過最on9既原因就係話 &rdquo; 我鍾意現兜兜畀錢嘅感覺 覺得實在啲&rdquo;"},{"pid":"13044c2e165fb1e283a0c8cebb3fdc1ff1f59350","tid":1180704,"uid":227275,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T04:58:10.000Z","msg":"最撚ON9係搵完散紙比完錢又要找錢<br />\n最後又拎張8達通出黎儲分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d80aadb6ff466512c09e5641a224fd1bdbec5ea","tid":1180704,"uid":45007,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T04:59:48.000Z","msg":"鐘意用cash關你咩事<br />\n用信用卡都唔快得過用cash好多"},{"pid":"ed61cf48f437172dbb29654b5e9b934a69b9982f","tid":1180704,"uid":84673,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:02:01.000Z","msg":"其實依家係大陸直頭唔洗帶銀包添啦<br />\n係街市買幾蚊菜買魚買肉都用支付寶/微信支付<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77820daf7b93a9e3ed370bfd33f77e142538ab70","tid":1180704,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ed61cf48f437172dbb29654b5e9b934a69b9982f","tid":1180704,"uid":84673,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"reply